f searches forward
F searches backwards
dfs will delete upto the next f

c change command
cc change line


:map + ddp     has the effect of moving a line up

:match ErrorMsg /\%>73v.\+/ has the effect of highlighting any characters over 73 with 
  the Error message background highlight

!!!  instant file explorer
:Sex

:highlight Normal ctermfg=grey ctermbg=darkblue   this will produce a blue background and grey font


